BitcoinPay is a bitcoin payment gateway allowing merchants to accept Bitcoins in form of payments on their websited or in retail stores. BitcoinPay is a startup company from the Czech republic supported by JIC accelerator.

* POS bitcoin payment terminal
* Powerfull API
* Reach - Europe
* Payout currencies (EUR, CZK, PLN, BTC)

